<a id="tokenomics"></a>
## 4  Tokenomics 101 ğŸ’

| Parameter | Value | Rationale |
|-----------|-------|-----------|
| Total supply | **1 000 000 000** `$AGIALPHA` | Immutable â€“ prevents unexpected inflation. |
| Utility | Escrow, staking, governance votes (voting power âˆ âˆšstake). |
| Fee burn | 1 % of each job reward is burned â†’ long-term deflation. |
| Minimum job reward | 10 000 `$AGIALPHA` (configurable) |
| Treasury | 5 % of burn redirected to Safety-&-Audit Fund |

*Detailed economic model will live in `docs/tokenomics_v1.pdf`.*

