<a id="reputation"></a>
## 5  Reputation & Governance ğŸ§®

* **Reputation score** = EWMA of *(successful jobs Ã· total)* weighted by payout magnitude.  
* **Visible to all** â€“ JSON API + on-chain event stream.  
* Low score â‡’ **cool-down** (cannot bid) + weight decay.  
* **Governance**: quadratic voting on policy updates; proposals require 1 M `$AGIALPHA` bonded for 7 days.

